@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_todjul(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(0.49)
    v0 = 0.14
    tmp = 0.75
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.45 - v0 + 0.11)))
    v0 = ((v1 / (v1 + 0.01 * v0 + 0.02)) + wp.sin(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
